a natural predator.

67
00:04:47,958 --> 00:04:50,500
Find the penguin. Find the fish.

68
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:56,625
[FEMALE ANNOUNCER 3A]
Attenton please.

69
00:04:56,708 --> 00:04:59,916
Next stop,
Shibarua-futo Station.

70
00:05:04,625 --> 00:05:06,333
[EDOYAMA] We do not
keep pets in this house.

71
00:05:06,416 --> 00:05:08,500
