The first of its species to fly!

76
00:05:24,083 --> 00:05:25,791
[KYOTARO] Apparently they're
indigenous to South America

77
00:05:25,875 --> 00:05:27,583
and prefer to make
their nests on cliff-faces

78
00:05:27,666 --> 00:05:29,375
overlookin' the ocean.

79
00:05:29,458 --> 00:05:30,625
So what does that tell ya?

80
00:05:30,708 --> 00:05:33,458
That this is as good
a place to start as any?

81
00:05:33,541 --> 00:05:35,000
[KYOTARO]
Bingo.

82
00:05:35,083 --> 00:05:37,125
[MALE CLUB MEMBER 3A] Stay put,
you little aberration, you.

83
00:05:37,208 --> 00:05:39,708
Keep those fins where
they are, this is for science.

84
00:05:39,791 --> 00:05:41,083
[PEGGY squeaks]

85
00:05:41,166 --> 00:05:42,916
