on the talk-show circuit.

86
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,625
Make a break for it, Peggy!

87
00:05:44,708 --> 00:05:45,583
[MALE CLUB MEMBERS gasp]

88
00:05:45,666 --> 00:05:48,916
[PEGGY squeals]

89
00:05:50,666 --> 00:05:54,500
Heads up! There it is!
Wait, what the hell?

90
00:05:56,708 --> 00:05:58,666
[screams]

91
00:05:59,208 --> 00:06:00,375
[MALE CLUB MEMBER 3C]
No sweat, boys!

92
00:06:00,458 --> 00:06:02,208
Little Birdie's in the nest!

93
00:06:02,291 --> 00:06:03,625
[RINKA]
Right! Let's do this!

94
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:04,916
[KYOTARO grunts]

95
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:12,083
I'm not gonna let you
do anything to my Peggy!

96
00:06:12,166 --> 00:06:13,875
Uh, fellahs,
she's talkin' to me.

97
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:15,375
Stay out of this, young lady.

98
00:06:15,458 --> 00:06:17,250
Fat chance of that, creep!

99
00:06:17,333 --> 00:06:19,583
Quit bein' an ass-pain
and hand over the squawker!

100
00:06:19,666 --> 00:06:22,708
