Pull over right now!

101
00:06:22,791 --> 00:06:24,958
[PEGGY sqeaks]
[MALE CLUB MEMBER 3A groans]

102
00:06:29,041 --> 00:06:31,000
[KYOTARO]
You're up, Rinka. Stay focused.

103
00:06:31,083 --> 00:06:32,833
I got this.

104
00:06:34,875 --> 00:06:37,583
[MALE CLUB MEMBER 3B]
Knock it off!

105
00:06:37,666 --> 00:06:39,375
Hurry! Grab my hand!

106
00:06:44,166 --> 00:06:46,041
[ALL yell]

107
00:06:50,208 --> 00:06:51,875
Get us out of here!

108
00:06:53,708 --> 00:06:54,958
[KYOTARO]
How many people inside?

109
