I think it's just three.

110
00:07:01,083 --> 00:07:05,416
[MALE CLUB MEMBERS yelling]

111
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,833
[OLD LADIES gasping]

112
00:07:06,916 --> 00:07:07,500
Kyotaro!

113
