116
00:07:22,375 --> 00:07:24,916
Don't tell me this is
how I'm gonna go out.

117
00:07:27,708 --> 00:07:28,708
[KYOTARO]
And I was just starting

118
00:07:28,791 --> 00:07:30,708
to get somewhere with her, too.

119
00:07:30,791 --> 00:07:33,458
