120
00:07:36,083 --> 00:07:38,875
[PEGGY whining]

121
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:48,166
[MURASAKI]
I saw Peggy for the first time

122
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,875
on the way home from school.

123
00:07:49,958 --> 00:07:51,958
I was sitting on the train,
nose in a book.

124
00:07:52,041 --> 00:07:54,166
[PEGGY cooing]

125
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:56,041
Oh!

126
00:07:56,125 --> 00:07:58,291
Here you go, sweetie,
bon appétit.

127
00:07:58,375 --> 00:08:01,291
[PEGGY cooing]

128
