what you know about me

135
00:08:21,458 --> 00:08:22,791
and my friend on the D.L.

136
00:08:22,875 --> 00:08:24,708
I imagine it'd cause quite
a stir if people knew

137
00:08:24,791 --> 00:08:26,125
about the two of you.

138
00:08:26,208 --> 00:08:28,083
[RINKA]
Yeah. No joke.

139
00:08:28,166 --> 00:08:30,291
You guys are the coolest
people I've ever met!

140
00:08:30,375 --> 00:08:32,458
You're like super heroes
or something!

141
00:08:32,541 --> 00:08:34,000
[KYOTARO]
Hm.

142
00:08:38,708 --> 00:08:41,708
She thinks we're like heroes.

143
00:08:41,791 --> 00:08:43,250
[KYOTARO] Well, you do
have a lot of potential

144
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:45,583
in that area, you know.

145
00:08:45,666 --> 00:08:47,250
Look, you're very sweet, but...

146
00:08:47,333 --> 00:08:50,291
The vigilante thing
isn't my bag.

147
00:08:50,375 --> 00:08:52,125
Let me ask you something, Rinka.

148
00:08:52,208 --> 00:08:55,166
Do you know what it's like to
live every day without hope?

149
00:08:57,875 --> 00:08:59,333
[CROWD gasps]

150
00:09:01,583 --> 00:09:03,083
[KYOTARO]
Where I grew up,

151
00:09:03,166 --> 00:09:06,958
if you were at the bottom of the
food chain, that's how it was.

152
00:09:07,041 --> 00:09:09,458
The idea of a hero was
an unfathomable concept

153
00:09:09,541 --> 00:09:13,166
to me when I was a kid.

154
00:09:13,250 --> 00:09:14,416
But, then...

155
00:09:14,500 --> 00:09:17,708
Meeting you six months ago
changed all that.

156
00:09:17,791 --> 00:09:18,958
It's like...

157
00:09:19,041 --> 00:09:22,416
For the first time in
my life, I knew hope.

158
00:09:24,458 --> 00:09:26,250
Anyway, see ya tomorrow.

159
00:09:28,083 --> 00:09:29,958
We met six months ago?

160
00:09:30,041 --> 00:09:31,250
[PEGGY]
Wah!

161
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:33,875
[MALE ANNOUNCER 3A] Dramatic
accident on Rainbow Bridge

162
00:09:33,958 --> 00:09:35,333
this afternoon.

163
00:09:35,416 --> 00:09:37,500
Witnesses claim to have seen
a man in a crow-like mask

164
00:09:37,583 --> 00:09:40,041
accompanied by a
mysterious albino girl,

165
00:09:40,125 --> 00:09:42,541
both said to have used
some sort of, quote: "super"...

166
00:09:42,625 --> 00:09:44,041
[RINKA groans]

167
00:09:44,125 --> 00:09:46,250
We've gone through
this whole bag of rice!

168
00:09:46,333 --> 00:09:47,333
